<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 06:17:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据韩联社报道，韩国、中国、日本将于5月26日至27日在首尔举行峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-hold-summit-seoul-may-26-27-reports-yonhap-2024-05-23/</link><description>韩联社周四称，韩国、中国和日本领导人将于 5 月 26 日至 27 日在首尔举行三边峰会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 05:44:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-hold-summit-seoul-may-26-27-reports-yonhap-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国联想延续收入增长势头，超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-lenovo-extends-revenue-growth-streak-beats-expectations-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国联想集团周四公布第四季度营收增长 9%，达到 138 亿美元，这家全球最大的个人电脑 (PC) 制造商摆脱了 COVID-19 大流行后的需求低迷。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 04:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-lenovo-extends-revenue-growth-streak-beats-expectations-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>有关中国在台湾周边进行军事演习的关键引述</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，中国在台湾周围开始为期两天的“惩罚”演习，据称这是对“分裂主义行为”的回应，以及台湾新总统赖清德发表就职演说后，台湾军方动员了军队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 04:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国将军称中国军队于2023年进行了入侵台湾演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</link><description>一名驻该地区的美国高级将领周四表示，中国 2023 年在台湾海峡举行的军事演习演练了入侵该岛的关键演习，尽管实际的攻击并非迫在眉睫或不可避免。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市走软，各国央行保持耐心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</link><description>由于市场消化了主要经济体政策制定者在通胀高企的情况下倾向于采取耐心的货币宽松政策的影响，数个亚洲股市基准周四下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国哈尔滨公寓楼发生爆炸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周四上午报道，中国黑龙江省省会哈尔滨市一栋五层公寓楼发生爆炸，目前没有人员伤亡报告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美联储会议纪要鹰派，美元徘徊在一周高位附近；猕猴桃公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，美元兑主要货币汇率创本月最佳表现，周四徘徊在一周高点附近，此前美联储上次会议纪要显示部分官员愿意加息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在台湾周边展开“惩罚”兵棋推演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</link><description>愤怒的中国周四在台湾周围发起了“惩罚”演习，据称这是对“分裂主义行为”的回应，在官方媒体谴责新就职的总统赖清德之际，派出全副武装的战机并进行模拟袭击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>桥水基金任命中国区总裁阿尔珀特负责监管新投资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</link><description>桥水基金已提拔其中国区总经理乔安娜·阿尔珀特 (Joanna Alpert) 担任最近成立的业务部门负责人，该部门专注于管理和创造新的投资产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：韩国银行紧随其后，英伟达继续前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>杜邦公司将分拆为三个公司，并更换首席执行官埃德·布林 (Ed Breen)</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</link><description>杜邦公司周三表示，将分拆为三家上市公司，其股价在盘后上涨 5%，加入众多寻求释放价值和追求集中增长的美国企业集团行列。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，因国家监管机构审查而推迟波音向中国交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位知情人士告诉路透社，由于中国对驾驶舱录音机电池进行监管审查，波音向中国的飞机交付最近几周被推迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国多个城市大幅降低还款额和抵押贷款利率以刺激房地产需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国多个城市降低了首付和抵押贷款利率，以应对最新一波刺激低迷房地产需求的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>Temu母公司拼多多控股第一季度营收超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</link><description>拼多多控股周三超出了第一季度收入预期，这得益于其国际购物网站 Temu 以及消费者对其中国折扣电子商务平台拼多多日益增长的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人郭文贵因诈骗罪受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</link><description>对流亡中国商人郭文贵的刑事审判将于周三开始陪审团遴选，美国检察官指控郭文贵诈骗数千名投资者和支持者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>